  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 27-7-5, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO RESCIND THE REDUCTION OF THE STATE INCOME TAX; TO REPEAL SECTION 27-7-5.1, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, WHICH PROVIDES FOR THE REDUCTION OF THE TAX ON ALL TAXABLE INCOME IN EXCESS OF $10,000.00, UNDER CERTAIN CONDITIONS, BEGINNING IN 2031; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
